node.text:
For #WorldRefugeeDay, I got the chance to swap stories of home with an incredible person. @mi.nnie_san lives in Denver, but was born in a refugee camp.⁣
⁣
It was a moving experience for me and a reminder that we all have a part to play making sure @refugees feel welcome.⁣
⁣
#WithRefugees #RefugeeDay

node.text: I am in New York promoting @neverhaveiever but we had a @goldhouseco event in LA and I missed seeing these beauties. This amazing group of talented South Asian actors and creatives took time out of their busy schedules to support the show and it means the world to me. Our cast and writers look up to these guys and I don’t know, it just hits different when the support comes from our own community. Love you guys. Thanks. ❤️
